value:
Breweries/Units of the Company are accredited with various certifications.

1) All Units/Breweries of the Company are in conformance with international standards and have been accredited with certifications like (a) Heineken Total Productivity Maintenance (HTPM) for Quality Management System; (b) ISO 22000:2018 (Food Safety Management System);

2) For ISO 45001:2018 (Safety Management System) and ISO 14001:2015 (Environmental Management System), the company covered seven breweries out of 19 breweries. ISO 50001:2018 (Energy Management System)

